# 🔐 Password Generator

A lightweight and secure *Password Generator* built with Python.  
This tool helps you create strong and random passwords using a combination of uppercase, lowercase, digits, and symbols.

---

## ✨ Features
- 🔑 Generate random passwords of any length  
- 🔒 Includes letters, digits, and special characters for security  
- ⚡ Default length = 12 characters (recommended minimum)  
- 🎯 Easy to run from terminal — no extra libraries needed  

