## 🚀 Getting Started

### 1. Clone the repository
bash
git clone https://github.com/<your-username>/password-generator.git
cd password-generator


### 2. Run the script
bash
python password_generator.py


### 3. Enter desired length
Example:

Enter password length (default 12): 16
Generated password: 4^ApYhZ7@tQ9wB#f


👉 If you just press *Enter*, it will generate a 12-character password by default.

